      • makeError

        public static void makeError(org.sonatype.plexus.build.incremental.BuildContext buildContext,
                             File file,
                             String message,
                             boolean throwErrors)
                      throws org.apache.maven.plugin.MojoExecutionException
        Produces a project error message. If run in an IDE this will produce an error marker on the affected file, if this is run as a Maven CLI build the error marker has no affect, but if throwErrors is set to true this will produce an exception that will fail the Maven build with the given message.
        Parameters:
        buildContext - - The current maven build context.
        file - - The file that the error is seen in.
        message - - The error message.
        throwErrors - - true to raise an exception which will fail the build at the current point, false to simply tag the file with an error marker.
        Throws:
        org.apache.maven.plugin.MojoExecutionException - - If throwErrors=true this exception will be thrown.

      • makeError

        public static void makeError(org.sonatype.plexus.build.incremental.BuildContext buildContext,

                             Throwable e,

                      throws org.apache.maven.plugin.MojoExecutionException
        Produces a project error message. If run in an IDE this will produce an error marker on the affected file, if this is run as a Maven CLI build the error marker has no affect, but if throwErrors is set to true this will produce an exception that will fail the Maven build with the given message.
        Parameters:
        buildContext - - The current maven build context.
        file - - The file that the error is seen in.
        message - - The error message.
        lineNumber - - The line number of the file the error is seen on. 0 if unknown, 1 for the first line.
        columnNumber - - The column number of the file the error is seen on. 0 if unknown, 1 for the first column.
        e - - The cause, can be null.
        throwErrors - - true to raise an exception which will fail the build at the current point, false to simply tag the file with an error marker.
        Throws:
        org.apache.maven.plugin.MojoExecutionException - - If throwErrors=true this exception will be thrown.
